stream = StringIO()
printer = PythonPrinter(stream)
for line in ['try:', 'elsemyvar = 12', 'if True:', "print 'hi'", None,
    'finally:', 'dosomething', None]:
    printer.writeline(line)
assert stream.getvalue(
    ) == """try:
    elsemyvar = 12
    if True:
        print 'hi'
finally:
    dosomething
""", stream.getvalue(
    )
